Package: vcrpart
Type: Package
Title: Tree-based varying coefficient regression for generalized linear and ordinal mixed models
Version: 0.1-15
Date: 2014-09-05
Authors@R: c(
  person("Reto", "Buergin", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "rbuergin@gmx.ch"),
  person("Gilbert", "Ritschard", role = c("ctb", "ths"), 
         email = "gilbert.ritschard@unige.ch"))
Maintainer: Reto Buergin <rbuergin@gmx.ch>
Description: The package provides a recursive partitioning algorithm for varying coefficient generalized linear models (GLM) and ordinal 2-stage linear mixed models (OLMM). Special features are coefficient-wise partitioning and non-varying coefficients.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 2.12.1), parallel, partykit
Imports: stats, graphics, methods, nlme, rpart, numDeriv, ucminf, zoo, sandwich, strucchange
LazyLoad: yes
NeedsCompilation: yes
Packaged: 2014-09-05 09:00:00 UTC; rbuergin
